<div class="index">
  <div class="hero">
    <img id="hero-image" src="/assets/hero-image.jpg" />
    <div class="hero-logo">Made with Sol</div>
  </div>

  <div class="about">
    <div class="polaroid-container">
      <div class="polaroid-back"></div>
      <img class="about-image" src="/assets/lelou.jpg" alt="About Us" />
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Hi Y 'all!</h2>
      <p>I’m Lelou, the hands behind Solspun Threads!</br>
        When I’m not stitching up new designs, you’ll find me crocheting,
        wandering antique shops, or reading in the sun with my dog by my
        side. I make things intentionally — with care, feeling, and a love for
        slow creation woven into every piece. So glad you’re here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="shop-cta">
    <h2 class="section-title">Made with Sol</h2>
    <div class="solspun-descriptions">
      <p>soft</p>
      <p>rooted in emotion</p>
      <p>intentional</p>
    </div>
    <div class="shop-item">
      <img src="/assets/tote.jpg" alt="Shop Item 1" />
      <div class="shop-item-text">
        <h3>Canvas Tote Bag</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/product/canvas-tote-bag" class="shop-cta-button">shop now</a>
  </div>

  <div class="solspun-details">
    <div class="solspun-details-item">
      <img src="/assets/button.png" alt="button-icon" />
      <p>Each piece begins at my sewing table, where I pattern, draft, cut, and stitch with care.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="solspun-details-item">
      <img src="/assets/hand-crafted.png" alt="hand-crafted-icon" />
      <p>
        100% made in house.
        Crafted with intention and a deep love for
        thoughtful, slow creation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="solspun-details-item">
      <img src="/assets/machine.png" alt="button-icon" />
      <p>
        Designs are dreamed up, digitized, and stitched by
        me using my own embroidery machine—bringing
        thread to life, one stitch at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

